						               													<description>CARD Trip is a unique game allowing you to discover a city by making a 3-day trip with playing cards.&amp;#10;With its simple game system: Draw / Place / Discard, start a game alone or with your loved ones in 5 minutes to make the best stay!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of CARD Trip is to make the best stay by playing and combining cards from Collections, Activities, Relaxations and Discoveries. These categories allow you to score points in a variety of ways and to interact with other players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The stay lasts 3 days and each day is divided into 4 phases: morning, noon, afternoon and evening. At each phase of the day and in turn, the players draw a card, place one face down and discard another. Each player's laid cards form a line representing their stay.&amp;#10; At the end of the game, the total score of the players is calculated by counting the points of the cards in each category. To win: accumulate different Collection cards, play the same types of Activities as the others, share meals or rest with Relaxations and be the only one to make unique Discoveries.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
